          <para>Is the 32-bit name of the source general-purpose register or stack pointer, encoded in the "Rn" field.</para>
        </intro>
      </account>
    </explanation>
    <explanation enclist="ADDS_32S_addsub_imm, ADDS_64S_addsub_imm" symboldefcount="1">
